      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Edge Authoring Golden Path Checklist\n\nGoal: prove the minimum edge workflow from a blank graph:\n- draw a `relationship` edge (`plain.edge`)\n- import the edge class library\n- upgrade the edge to a class-backed edge via the edge type selector\n\nHow to use:\n- Walk step-by-step from **Step 1** onward.\n- Mark each step **PASS** or **FAIL**.\n- If a step fails, write a minimal repro note."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "edge-authoring-checklist-known-refs",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Known Refs",
      "position": {
        "x": 80,
        "y": -760
