      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Known Good Target Refs\n\n- Edge class library: `/library/classes/edges/root.node#root`\n- Edge class smoke test: `/tasks/graph-organization/edge-class-contract/edge-class-bridge-smoke.node#root`\n\nIf a ref fails to resolve, capture diagnostics from the bridge properties panel."
      }
    },
